### Create recovery plan
POST {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}:{{$dotenv PORT}}/recovery-plan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv API_TOKEN}}

{
  "input": "I need help with recovery planning"
}

### Create recovery plan with userId — response includes logId for GET /logs and PATCH /logs/:id/done
POST {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}:{{$dotenv PORT}}/recovery-plan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv API_TOKEN}}

{
  "input": "I need help with recovery planning",
  "userId": "{{$dotenv USER_UUID}}"
}

### Missing token
POST {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}:{{$dotenv PORT}}/recovery-plan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "This should fail without a token"
}

### Invalid token
POST {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}:{{$dotenv PORT}}/recovery-plan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer wrong-token

{
  "input": "This should fail with a bad token"
}
